<p>TJ first wrote the enemies of Great Britain, then struck out of Great Britain and added ir to the.</p></div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#TSJN-01-01-0113-fn-0017-ptr" id="TSJN-01-01-0113-fn-0017">17</a>
<p>In both places TJ first wrote to and then, after changing the subsequent phrase, wrote for over to.</p></div>
</div>
